(3)Describe the differences between forks, clones, and branches.  When would you use one instead of another?

Ans:
forks copy a repository one gitHub account to another, clones copy a repository from gitHub account to a local computer or one local computer to another local comuter , branch are used to creating or exploring different feature in the same repository whether i located in a local computer or in gitHub account

